snippet.title: Seeing Things - Launch Trailer
snippet.description: Spot and uncover over 500 creepy and comical anomalies in Seeing Things, a surveillance horror game. You command the surveillance camera across three difficulty settings. Observe, detect, survive! https://store.steampowered.com/app/2636340/Seeing_Things/
